<hometopic>Calendar Help
<abbrev>Calendar Help

				<idx>calendar, using<\idx>
				<idx>starting calendar<\idx>

				<idx>introduction<\idx>

Use the desktop Calendar to schedule appointments and group meetings, 
make To Do and appointment lists, and set appointment reminders.

<procedure>To Open Calendar

<p>Click the Calendar control in the Front Panel.

<newline>&empty;<newline>

<figure nonumber entity=Calendar-Icon>
<\figure>

<newline>&empty;<newline>

<p>Calendar displays Month view by default.  
